$ Oracle: V$STATISTICS_LEVEL
@ v$statistics_level

`v$statistics_level` displays status-information about the statistics and advisories that are controlled by the
→ development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters[init parameter]
→ development/databases/Oracle/adminstration/init-parameters/statistics_level[`statistics_level`].

